tweet_text:
Today's 2nd dose of the Pfizer/Bio-N-Tech Covid-19 vaccine went without any problems or complications.

I felt a minor jump-start anxiety reaction for a few moments, but that is expected when your immune system revs up to fight any pathogen. 

#COVIDVaccination
text_en: Today's nd dose of the Pfizer/Bio-N-Tech Covid-19 vaccine went without any problems or complications. I felt a minor jump-start anxiety reaction for a few moments, but that is expected when your immune system revs up to fight any pathogen.

tweet_text:
The weeks that went by until this very day saw my chronic fatigue improve somewhat, my anxiety level fell quite a bit, and I slept better than recent years since I could breathe better. 

The first night, I had a serious case of the munchies. 

#COVIDVaccination #Munchies
text_en: The weeks that went by until this very day saw my chronic fatigue improve somewhat, my anxiety level fell quite a bit, and I slept better than recent years since I could breathe better. The first night, I had a serious case of the munchies.

tweet_text:
With a couple of cold packs, some clear, cold liquids, and some rest I was good to go by later that same night and I slept well. 

The next day I had a sore arm, but it wasn't bad. 

I also experienced an IMPROVEMENT in my ability to breathe. 

#COVIDVaccination
text_en: With a couple of cold packs, some clear, cold liquids, and some rest I was good to go by later that same night and I slept well. The next day I had a sore arm, but it wasn't bad. I also experienced an IMPROVEMENT in my ability to breathe.

tweet_text:
My heart was beating kinda funny (fast), and I felt suddenly really hot, sweaty, really fatigued, and kinda like I was having a panic attack. This lasted a short time, just less than an hour. The fatigue held on for a few hours, though. 

#COVIDVaccination

Then it came my turn. On 27 August 2021, I had my first Pfizer/Bio-N-Tech Covid vaccine. Within exactly 10 minutes, I experienced a sensation of being hyper-alert as if I might be in the beginning stage of an allergic reaction.

#COVIDVaccination
text_en: Then it came my turn. On August , I had my first Pfizer/Bio-N-Tech Covid vaccine. Within exactly minutes, I experienced a sensation of being hyper-alert as if I might be in the beginning stage of an allergic reaction.

tweet_text:
I have other people in my house who were at equally high risk for serious long-term injury or death from Covid, and so I told them to get the vaccine first so as to save their lives and lessen my risk while we watched for any dangerous after-effects. 

#COVIDVaccination
text_en: I have other people in my house who were at equally high risk for serious long-term injury or death from Covid, and so I told them to get the vaccine first so as to save their lives and lessen my risk while we watched for any dangerous after-effects.

tweet_text:
BUT....I was smart, and I watched the CDC research on the Covid vaccine, and I listened to ACTUAL DOCTORS and other MEDICAL PROFESSIONALS who are experts in infectious diseases, virology, etc. I then spoke with my pharmacist who informed me I was safe. 

#COVIDVaccination
